'''锰(V)酸钾'''（K<sub>3</sub>MnO<sub>4</sub>）是一种淡蓝色的盐，它是很少见的[[次锰酸盐|次锰酸盐]]。

== 制备 ==
最早制得的锰(V)酸盐是Na<sub>3</sub>MnO<sub>4</sub>·10H<sub>2</sub>O，但后来发现它实际上是Na<sub>3</sub>MnO<sub>4</sub>·0.25NaOH·10H<sub>2</sub>O。<ref name=wc>{{cite book|title=《无机化学丛书》第九卷：锰分族、铁系、铂系|pages=P46-47|isbn=7-03-002238-6|location=北京|publisher=科学出版社}}</ref>

*用过量的[[亚硫酸钾|亚硫酸钾]]还原[[高锰酸钾|高锰酸钾]]：<ref name="C&W">{{Cotton&Wilkinson4th|page=746}}.</ref><ref name="G&E">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw1st|pages=1221–22}}.</ref>
::MnO{{su|b=4|p=−}} + SO{{su|b=3|p=2−}} + H<sub>2</sub>O → MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}} + SO{{su|b=4|p=2−}} + {{nowrap|2 H<sup>+</sup>}}
*[[锰酸钾|锰酸钾]]与[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]在10mol/L的[[氢氧化钾|氢氧化钾]]溶液中反应：<ref>{{citation | title = Oxidation of hydrocarbons. 18. Mechanism of the reaction between permanganate and carbon-carbon double bonds | first1 = Donald G. | last1 = Lee | first2 = Tao | last2 = Chen | journal = J. Am. Chem. Soc. | year = 1989 | volume = 111 | issue = 19 | pages = 7534–38 | doi =  10.1021/ja00201a039}}.</ref>
::{{nowrap|2 MnO{{su|b=4|p=2−}}}} + H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub> + {{nowrap|2 OH<sup>−</sup>}} → {{nowrap|2 MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}}}} + O<sub>2</sub> + {{nowrap|2 H<sub>2</sub>O}}
*在3-10mol/L的氢氧化钾溶液中用[[扁桃酸|扁桃酸]]还原锰酸钾：<ref name="Mandelate"/>
::{{nowrap|2 MnO{{su|b=4|p=2−}}}} + C{{su|b=8}}H{{su|b=7}}O{{su|b=3|p=−}} + {{nowrap|2 OH<sup>−</sup>}} → {{nowrap|2 MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}}}} + C{{su|b=8}}H{{su|b=5}}O{{su|b=3|p=−}} + {{nowrap|2 H<sub>2</sub>O}}
*[[二氧化锰|二氧化锰]]在浓氢氧化钾溶液中歧化：<ref name="C&W"/>
::{{nowrap|2 MnO<sub>2</sub>}} + {{nowrap|3 OH<sup>−</sup>}} → MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}} + MnO(OH) + H<sub>2</sub>O

== 性质 ==
锰(V)酸盐在无水和无二氧化碳的条件下能稳定存在。在水溶液中因歧化而不稳定，尤其是在碱性溶液中。<ref name="C&W"/><ref name="G&E"/>估计pH=14的水溶液中它的[[标准电极电势|标准电极电势]]如下所示：<ref>{{RubberBible62nd|page=D-134}}.</ref><ref>{{citation | title = Manganese – compounds – standard reduction potentials | url = http://www.webelements.com/manganese/compounds.html | publisher = WebElements | accessdate = 2010-06-26 | archive-date = 2021-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117221000/https://webelements.com/manganese/compounds.html | dead-url = no }}.</ref><ref name="Epot">{{citation | title = Rate of the MnO<sub>4</sub><sup>−</sup>/MnO<sub>4</sub><sup>2−</sup> and MnO<sub>4</sub><sup>2−</sup>/MnO<sub>4</sub><sup>3−</sup> electrode reactions in alkaline solutions at solid electrodes | first1 = K. | last1 = Sekula-Brzezińska | first2 = P. K. | last2 = Wrona | first3 = Z. | last3 = Galus | journal = Electrochim. Acta | volume = 24 | issue = 5 | pages = 555–63 | doi = 10.1016/0013-4686(79)85032-X | year = 1979}}.</ref>
:MnO{{su|b=4|p=2−}} + e<sup>−</sup> {{eqm}} MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}}   ''E'' = +0.27 V
:MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}} + e<sup>−</sup> + {{nowrap|4 H<sub>2</sub>O}} {{eqm}} MnO<sub>2</sub> + {{nowrap|6 OH<sup>−</sup>}}   ''E'' = +0.96 V
歧化反应被认为经过质子化的中间体，<ref name="Epot"/>因为HMnO{{su|b=4|p=2−}} {{eqm}} MnO{{su|b=4|p=3−}} + H<sup>+</sup>的[[酸度系数|酸度系数]]的负对数，即p''K''<sub>a</sub>约为{{nowrap|13.7 ± 0.2}}。<ref>{{citation | title = Studies of Manganate(V), -(VI), and -(VII) Tetraoxyanions by Pulse Radiolysis. Optical Spectra of Protonated Forms | first1 = J. D. | last1 = Rush | first2 = B. H. J. | last2 = Bielski | journal = Inorg. Chem. | year = 1995 | volume = 34 | issue = 23 | pages = 5832–38 | doi = 10.1021/ic00127a022}}.</ref>然而，K<sub>3</sub>MnO<sub>4</sub>能与Ca<sub>2</sub>Cl(PO<sub>4</sub>)[[共结晶|共结晶]]并析出，使得人们可以用[[紫外可见吸收光谱|紫外可见吸收光谱]]来研究锰(V)酸根离子。<ref name="C&W"/><ref>{{citation | journal = J. Chem. Soc. | year = 1956 | pages = 3373–80 | doi =   10.1039/JR9560003373 | title = Structure and reactivity of the oxy-anions of transition metals. Part I. The manganese oxy-anions | first1 = A. | last1 = Carrington | first2 = M. C. R. | last2 = Symons}}.</ref>

用高锰酸钾或锰酸钾氧化有机化合物时，锰(V)酸根离子经常作为中间体出现。<ref name=wc />

